Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: -DIRECTIONS: Heading North on Mathis Ferry Rd, take left on Whipple Road. Property is on right .5 miles from Mathis Ferry. OR Heading North on Long Point, take right on Whipple Road. Property is on left.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Excellent opportunity to occupy Beautiful Class A office space in Mount Pleasant. This recently built office park boasts a nice quiet setting on the main corridor between Hwy 17 and Long Point. Easy access to anywhere! Available space has high end finishes with custom lighting and a very large conference with lots of natural light!

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Minutes from I-526, SC Wando Port Terminal and less than 10 miles from downtown Charleston.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Small medical office condo in conveniently located Long Point Office Park.. Nearby amenities include Bell Hall Shopping Center, a Harris Teeter Grocery Store, Food Lion, Starbucks Coffee, Dry Cleaners, Daycare and much more.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Small medical office condo in conveniently located Long Point Office Park.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Intersection of Hwy 17 and Bowman Road close to East Cooper Medical  Center.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Multi-tenant office building located off Johnnie Dodds Blvd at the intersection of Hwy 17 and Bowman Road, in the heart of Mt. Pleasant. Close proximity to East Cooper Regional Medical Center, East Cooper Medical Center has had recent lobby renovations, offers ample surface parking at entrance to building, and is well lighted and nicely landscaped.

The space is leased to a medical user, however it would make excellent general office space. Other building occupants include attorney, banks, & medical.

Tenant pays their own power bill. Water and sewer is provided. Inside janitorial is not included but available.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Multi-tenant office building located off Johnnie Dodds Blvd.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Beautiful Class A brick office park in Mt. Pleasant adjacent to Belle Hall Housing Development. Two 8,000 square foot office condo buildings currently exist with two more in construction stage. A second floor 2,000 square foot office condo is available for lease. Elevators, interior stairs and plenty of parking round out this well cared for high end office park. The office has 4 large private offices(windowed), a larger conference room/office, 8 permanent cubicles with built in desks, tiled floor reception area and kitchenette, two restrooms and a copy room. A small space set to handle a large # of employees.

One suite available in Long Point Medical Campus.  Located in Mt Pleasant on Long Point Rd. near I-526 and Belle Hall.

Suite 101 is available now.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 1,717 SF Medical Office Space with well-designed layout.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: This 17,163 rentable square foot suite is on the second floor of 11 eWall Street. The building is set in an wooded site on a large pond that feels like its located in a rural setting while it is located in the heart of Mt. Pleasant. The suite contains 28 private offices, large conference room and private restrooms. It also provided a large open space in the center for the open office plan. The space may be leased fully furnished or without the furniture. The suite is available for sublease from January 1, 2018 to July 31, 2025.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Class A office space available in the heart of Mt. Pleasant.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Between 17 and Coleman Boulevard just over the Ravenel Bridge.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Subdivide-able ground floor office suite in Mt. Pleasant's most convenient location. Watermark Plaza is located minutes from downtown Charleston and just a short walk from amenities including Starbucks, Whole Foods and Mt. Pleasant's Waterfront Park. Renovations are underway on the building exterior and common area renovations have just been completed.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Subdivide-able ground floor office suite in Mt. Pleasant's most convenient location.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Watermark Plaza II is under going renovations now to include a new parking lot, new striping, new landscaping, new roof, and new exterior painting to make it one of the best office locations in Mt. Pleasant.
Nice office space in a great Mt. Pleasant location overlooking a lake. Tenant pays utilities, janitorial and increases in base year taxes, CAM and insurance.

Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: Located at the foot of the Ravenel Bridge just across from Memorial Waterfront Park near walking trails and an easy commute to downtown.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Class A office space for sublease in Mt. Pleasant. Sublease rate includes utilities and janitorial. Open area for workstations with many private offices. Conference room and large kitchen/break room. Lots of natural light.
